page.title: 14TRAFFIC AT CHANDLERS CORNER
page.content: We counted the traffic at the intersection of Drift Road, White Dirt Lane and Green Lane. In 15 minutes we saw 17 cars, 2 vans, 1 bicycle and 1 tractor in Green Lane; only 4 cars were seen in White Dirt Lane.
